View Historical Adherence Metrics

Discover how your schedules compare with how agents actually spent their time. To improve scheduling accuracy going forward, view the historical adherence dashboard.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

To view historical adherence metrics: Workforce Engagement Planner permission set

When your Salesforce admin turns on historical adherence, we analyze past schedules and how agents have spent working time. Historical adherence considers up to 365 days of past data.

From the App Launcher, click Historical Adherence.
If you donâ€™t see data right away, refresh the page, or return later. It can take some time to process historical data when your admin turns on this feature.
Select criteria to adjust the view.
You can filter metrics by time intervals, service territories, and job profiles.

We sync data hourly for the adherence dashboard. If you make changes such as renaming agents or job profiles, check back and refresh the dashboard to see the updated names.
title: Understanding Historical Adherence in Service Cloud
